show.description: A young CEO who discovers that two twins, one he is caring for and the other he finds on the street, look remarkably similar to his late fiancée. This discovery leads to a series of events that unravel the past, including the circumstances surrounding his fiancée's death and the mysterious connection between the twins and his life
